{"tid":1910922,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"出席飯局59名警員沒有感染　周二晚離開檢疫中心","createTime":"2020-03-05T04:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T04:17:56.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"367973e799addd5798ac0cf66e98ed4543341606","tid":1910922,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:00:59.000Z","msg":"一名早前確診新冠肺炎的男警，因發病後出席過飯局，導致飯局中59名警員被列為密切接觸者，需要接受檢疫隔離。警方今日(5日)表示，該59名曾與他聚餐的警務人員，已於3月3日晚上完成檢疫，離開檢疫中心。<br />\n<br />\n該名駐守北角警署的48歲許姓警員，他居於油美苑潤美閣的紀律部隊宿舍，2月18日曾去過多達60人的警察榮休飯局，2月20日確診新冠肺炎，出席飯局的59名警員隨即被衞生署界定為密切接觸者。 <br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200305/bkn-20200305025643826-0305_00822_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"c273b9ec9c75a14980701c8e1306ec94c54227e3","tid":1910922,"uid":2267,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fcJL6KU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfcJL6KU.jpg&h=b0728069&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5839bdfd0a1d2d2869712e629709834feaf37665","tid":1910922,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:08:28.000Z","msg":"國師話火化先好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0621ec17fcac8a0374fe8b24d157f873fb91a9","tid":1910922,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c273b9ec9c75a14980701c8e1306ec94c54227e3","tid":1910922,"uid":2267,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fcJL6KU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfcJL6KU.jpg&h=b0728069&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif